
<section class="home" id="home">
    <div class="content">
      <h3>Every <span>Batch</span> from Scratch</h3>
      <p>Sweet apple pie chocolate cake. Macaroon liquorice sweet. Red velvet with Strawberry-cum-cheese cake</p>
      <p style="color: black; font-size: 2.8rem; font-weight: bolder;"><i>A Little Bliss in Every Bite</i></p>
